snippet.title: Spy x Family Main Theme ELECTRO SWING VERSION ft. James Bond and Mission Impossible | tnbee mix

This OST played on Spy x Family, usually when Loid doing something related to his spy works.

Please use headphones or you are missing out a lot! 
Finally, anime covers are back on my channel! Feel free to listen to my other anime covers as well! Spy x Family is really wholesome and funny! Been really enjoying this anime lately! Also, leave a comment below if you have any anime cover requests!
